```
@Bean
public CommandLineRunner demo(String... args) {
    return (args) -&gt; {
    };
}
```

You are expecting to register a bean in Spring Container which implements **CommandLineRunner** interface so it can converted to lambda expression.
```
(args) -&gt; {};
```

